Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无限的时间将跳动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们悄声无息地燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界已经脱轨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被红世之火所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜和我在一起的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时开始像理所当然一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有时候夏娜看上去像个普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至会让我忘记她是火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和福里阿格雷一战以来的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却一口气把我从这浮夸的心情里拉回了现实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜是个强大又完美的火焰之雾这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,8)}{\bord2\1c&H3535FF&\3c&HCFCFCF&}纠缠的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和昨天一样 感觉杀意躲避攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知  知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么大力打也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不适当的用点力是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢的话快点躲掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在还没闭着眼睛锻炼过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然这样肯定不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果感觉杀意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单纯的攻击应该明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像知道对方要出什么的猜拳一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说猜拳什么的前一阵刚玩过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说得那么了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果输的一塌糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了吵死了吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锻炼中别说废话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等一下啊 搞突然袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击总是很突然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为说了废话才会那么丢脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了等下了 稍微等下也不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人可不会等的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是锻炼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找借口可很难看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是红世之徒的话你已经被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就到这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要准备去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  小悠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二自作主张结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为锻炼进行得不太顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢 好像给打得很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前更加不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却摆出一副悠然自得的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许察觉到自己比较差劲了也说不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差劲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜是那么可爱又小巧玲珑的女孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被打的四脚朝天 作为男孩子来说总有些丢脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我比较强 这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呢  男孩子都是爱面子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是在想让她看到优点的女孩子面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常想着悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是对悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放学以后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开封绝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微做些动作幅度大的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然做这么夸张的事没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了没问题才锻炼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为男孩子来说总有些丢脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要锻炼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就不丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这  算是在鼓励我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是说理所当然的话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说现在相当丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢脸什么的  这种无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是 悠二能变强然后一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有一元硬币的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去小卖部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐的情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但大姐恢复原样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会离开这个城市了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我是希望大姐恢复原样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇~~~这是一美做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友给了我料理的配方 就想试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小紫喜欢的话也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和外面卖的完全不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学料理很拿手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是爱好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了  图书管理员在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我和她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是图书馆的书今天要变更排放顺序了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后在图书馆集合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为每个班级要派两人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没空的话找个代替的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  要去探望外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家人都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那坂井  你和吉田同学一起去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上补习班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学 可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不添麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正规定两个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放学以后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开封绝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微做些动作幅度大的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和别人说好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  说过要借平井同学的笔记看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同学 下次好了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是我提出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因为是学校的委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上再锻炼也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过今天放学后做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今可说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锻炼才比较重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  但学校也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是我先提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才道歉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说要锻炼的不是悠二嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就今天一天有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二太没决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之今天就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有这么任性的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要参加委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二不锻炼不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为非常弱 非常丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像现在这样完全派不上用处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同学怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  完全没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说只是出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学  今天要和坂井一起加班了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 小夏娜一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天参加了委员会什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么 那在里面等如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了好吃的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜原来是一个人住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃  千草的也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  回去的时候和坂井独处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一没话题了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 刚才听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2班的平井同学测验全是100分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像体育课上也很厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真有呢 那样的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想问  关于小紫的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样总是一个人想下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么看待小紫的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然刚才3班的人也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真是厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 夏娜太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋 真是太没胆子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠真慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜都已经吃好饭洗完澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽是我以前的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小夏娜说我想穿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯  挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很晚了就送她回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果知道夏娜晚上住我房间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲会吓一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天份的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 反正已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙始终也只是个无聊的凡人么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红世之徒  对  只要来了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是火焰之雾也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要战斗的话 就算是悠二也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磷子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这封绝还真烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？身为悼词的咏唱者你不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就是这样了也没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一句话也说不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低谷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好 就交给小鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是要悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的  我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像错乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是失去主人的磷子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没几天也会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为磷子不管吞食了多少存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不能变成自己的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了主人的混蛋讨伐工具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我可不会被消灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  我要存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的  我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的身体软扑扑的真难砍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消除我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要砍 不要砍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有预定要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为从刚才开始就坐立不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是看外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不去也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为去也派不上用场的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这么说了吗
