Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在  存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么吃你都会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那么巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本体的核心却是很小的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在毁掉之前只有不断砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的存在还没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃的话  存在之力就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说没用的了
